  ('dietitian-moex-00149', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於次級訊息傳遞物（second messengers）之作用效應配對，下列何者錯誤？', '["2+ 鈣離子（Ca ）－活化蛋白激酶C（protein kinase C）", "環磷酸鳥苷（cGMP）－活化蛋白激酶A（protein kinase A）", "二醯甘油酯（DAG）－活化蛋白激酶C（protein kinase C）", "三磷酸肌醇（IP ）－釋出內質網（ER）的鈣離子至細胞質 3"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c8c7112f23f9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "925f56d717e3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "102", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00150', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '當暴露在有機磷（organophosphate）環境下，可能會對於神經肌肉接合處（neuromuscular junction）之神經肌肉傳導（neuromuscular transmission）造成什麼效應？', '["周邊神經釋放於突觸間隙（synaptic cleft）的乙醯膽鹼（acetylcholine）濃度會下降", "肌肉細胞膜會持續去極化（depolarization）而不再產生動作電位（action potential）", "活化更多肌肉細胞膜上電位閘控型鈉離子通道（voltage-gated sodium channel）", "促使乙醯膽鹼接受器敏感化（sensitization）而造成肌肉強直（tetanus）"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c8c7112f23f9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "925f56d717e3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "102", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00151', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於脂溶性訊息傳遞物（lipid-soluble messenger）的敘述，下列何者最適當？', '["細胞質內未被其結合之接受器均處於經常性活化狀態，以利於快速傳訊", "其接受器皆存在於細胞質中，需與其結合後，才能夠進入細胞核", "其接受器皆存在於細胞核中，兩者結合後會進行對基因轉錄之調節作用", "有些訊息傳遞物其接受器除了位於細胞內，也可位於細胞膜"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c8c7112f23f9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "925f56d717e3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "102", "s": "0203", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
